          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is your return policy?",
            "answer": "<p>We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee. If you're not completely happy with your purchase for any reason, contact our support team and we'll make it right with a full refund or replacement — no questions asked.</p>"
